        <p>Wawa built its first store in Washington D.C. and wanted to celebrate breaking into the new Market. This gorgeous store had 50‚Äù screens that the client wanted to use as a hands-on interactive history of Wawa. I was responsible for taking the PSDs from the creative team and adding 3D animation effect to the screen savers. Through various rounds of feedback and revisions, we landed with the video below.</p>
